## SsoConfig.dedupStorage property

Used by [SsoExecutionDialog](./teamsfx.ssoexecutiondialog.md) to remove duplicated messages, if not provided, it will use internal memory storage

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
dedupStorage?: Storage;
```
